able=\"false\" data-prefix=\"fas\" data-icon=\"calendar\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\"><path class=\"\" style=\"\" fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M12 192h424c6.6 0 12 5.4 12 12v260c0 26.5-21.5 48-48 48H48c-26.5 0-48-21.5-48-48V204c0-6.6 5.4-12 12-12zm436-44v-36c0-26.5-21.5-48-48-48h-48V12c0-6.6-5.4-12-12-12h-40c-6.6 0-12 5.4-12 12v52H160V12c0-6.6-5.4-12-12-12h-40c-6.6 0-12 5.4-12 12v52H48C21.5 64 0 85.5 0 112v36c0 6.6 5.4 12 12 12h424c6.6 0 12-5.4 12-12z\"></path></svg> 07/08/2026 by <span class=\"news-author\"><svg class=\"svg-inline--fa fa-user fa-w-14\" style=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" data-prefix=\"fas\" data-icon=\"user\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\"><path class=\"\" style=\"\" fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M224 256c70.7 0 128-57.3 128-128S294.7 0 224 0 96 57.3 96 128s57.3 128 128 128zm89.6 32h-16.7c-22.2 10.2-46.9 16-72.9 16s-50.6-5.8-72.9-16h-16.7C60.2 288 0 348.2 0 422.4V464c0 26.5 21.5 48 48 48h352c26.5 0 48-21.5 48-48v-41.6c0-74.2-60.2-134.4-134.4-134.4z\"></path></svg><span class=\"news-author-name\">Bitterblade</span></span></span></div><div class=\"content\"><p>July brings big updates to the forums!<br/>\n* The new <a href=\"https://pokemonrevolution.net/forum/index.php?app=proauctions&amp;module=auction&amp;controller=auctions\" rel=\"nofollow\">Trade Zone</a> is now live on the forums! This update brings a new, effecient way to navigate trades and features numerous, new filtering options. Please take some time to familarize yourself with these changes. The old Trade Zone will remain available until July 14 so that existing auctions can be completed, but it is no longer possible to start new threads there.<br/>\n* A World Quest starts July 11th during the day.<br/>\n* Tradable PvE Coin Shop items this month are: Salamence Mount, S Salamence Mount, Waluigi Hat, Waluigi Clothes</p>\n\n<p>Make sure to join our <a href=\"https://discord.gg/98pMNxq\" rel=\"nofollow\">Discord server</a> for news, updates, and more!</p>\n</div><!----></article><article><h5 class=\"title\"><svg class=\"svg-inline--fa fa-bullhorn fa-w-18 title-icon\" style=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" data-prefix=\"fas\" data-icon=\"bullhorn\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 576 512\"><path class=\"\" style=\"\" fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M576 240c0-23.63-12.95-44.04-32-55.12V32.01C544 23.26 537.02 0 512 0c-7.12 0-14.19 2.38-19.98 7.02l-85.03 68.03C364.28 109.19 310.66 128 256 128H64c-35.35 0-64 28.65-64 64v96c0 35.35 28.65 64 64 64h33.7c-1.39 10.48-2.18 21.14-2.18 32 0 39.77 9.26 77.35 25.56 110.94 5.19 10.69 16.52 17.06 28.4 17.06h74.28c26.05 0 41.69-29.84 25.9-50.56-16.4-21.52-26.15-48.36-26.15-77.44 0-11.11 1.62-21.79 4.41-32H256c54.66 0 108.28 18.81 150.98 52.95l85.03 68.03a32.023 32.023 0 0 0 19.98 7.02c24.92 0 32-22.78 32-32V295.13C563.05 284.04 576 263.63 576 240zm-96 141.42l-33.05-26.44C392.95 311.78 325.12 288 256 288v-96c69.12 0 136.95-23.78 190.95-66.98L480 98.58v282.84z\"></path></svg> Forum Upgrade: Invision 5 and Single Sign-On</h5><div class=\"news-meta-row\"><span class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"svg-inline--fa fa-tags fa-w-20\" style=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" data-prefix=\"fas\" data-icon=\"tags\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 640 512\"><path class=\"\" style=\"\" fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M497.941 225.941L286.059 14.059A48 48 0 0 0 252.118 0H48C21.49 0 0 21.49 0 48v204.118a48 48 0 0 0 14.059 33.941l211.882 211.882c18.744 18.745 49.136 18.746 67.882 0l204.118-204.118c18.745-18.745 18.745-49.137 0-67.882zM112 160c-26.51 0-48-21.49-48-48s21.49-48 48-48 48 21.49 48 48-21.49 48-48 48zm513.941 133.823L421.823 497.941c-18.745 18.745-49.137 18.745-67.882 0l-.36-.36L527.64 323.522c16.999-16.999 26.36-39.6 26.36-63.64s-9.362-46.641-26.36-63.64L331.397 0h48.721a48 48 0 0 1 33.941 14.059l211.882 211.882c18.745 18.745 18.745 49.137 0 67.882z\"></path></svg> Announcements</span><span class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"svg-inline--fa fa-calendar fa-w-14\" style=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" data-prefix=\"fas\" data-icon=\"calendar\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\"><path class=\"\" style=\"\" fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M12 192h424c6.6 0 12 5.4 12 12v260c0 26.5-21.5 48-48 48H48c-26.5 0-48-21.5-48-48V204c0-6.6 5.4-12 12-12zm436-44v-36c0-26.5-21.5-48-48-48h-48V12c0-6.6-5.4-12-12-12h-40c-6.6 0-12 5.4-12 12v52H160V12c0-6.6-5.4-12-12-12h-40c-6.6 0-12 5.4-12 12v52H48C21.5 64 0 85.5 0 112v36c0 6.6 5.4 12 12 12h424c6.6 0 12-5.4 12-12z\"></path></svg> 07/06/2026 by <span class=\"news-author\"><svg class=\"svg-inline--fa fa-user fa-w-14\" style=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" data-prefix=\"fas\" data-icon=\"user\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\"><path class=\"\" style=\"\" fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M224 256c70.7 0 128-57.3 128-128S294.7 0 224 0 96 57.3 96 128s57.3 128 128 128zm89.6 32h-16.7c-22.2 10.2-46.9 16-72.9 16s-50.6-5.8-72.9-16h-16.7C60.2 288 0 348.2 0 422.4V464c0 26.5 21.5 48 48 48h352c26.5 0 48-21.5 48-48v-41.6c0-74.2-60.2-134.4-134.4-134.4z\"></path></svg><span class=\"news-author-name\">Shaolan</span></span></span></div><div class=\"is-collapsed content\"><p>The forum has been upgraded from Invision 4 to Invision 5.<br/>\nThe upgrade to Invision 5 provides faster page load times, a modernized interface, and a improved responsive layout for mobile devices.</p>\n\n<h4>Single Sign-On (SSO) &amp; Session Renewal</h4>\n\n<p>The Dashboard, login system, and forum now share a single session. This eliminating the need for separate logins.</p>\n\n<h4>Session Management</h4>\n\n<p>Active sessions can now be managed from a single location. You can view or terminate active connections via the dashboard:</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://dashboard.pokemonrevolution.net/sessions\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dashboard Session page</a></p>\n\n<p>To improve account safety, security actions such as a password change, will now automatically invalidate and log out all other active sessions.</p>\n</div><button type=\"button\" class=\"news-toggle\"><svg class=\"svg-inline--fa fa-chevron-down fa-w-14\" style=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" data-prefix=\"fas\" data-icon=\"chevron-down\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\"><path class=\"\" style=\"\" fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M207.029 381.476L12.686 187.132c-9.373-9.373-9.373-24.569 0-33.941l22.667-22.667c9.357-9.357 24.522-9.375 33.901-.04L224 284.505l154.745-154.021c9.379-9.335 24.544-9.317 33.901.04l22.667 22.667c9.373 9.373 9.373 24.569 0 33.941L240.971 381.476c-9.373 9.372-24.569 9.372-33.942 0z\"></path></svg> Read more</button></article><article><h5 class=\"title\"><svg class=\"svg-inline--fa fa-bullhorn fa-w-18 title-icon\" style=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" data-prefix=\"fas\" data-icon=\"bullhorn\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 576 512\"><path class=\"\" style=\"\" fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M576 240c0-23.63-12.95-44.04-32-55.12V32.01C544 23.26 537.02 0 512 0c-7.12 0-14.19 2.38-19.98 7.02l-85.03 68.03C364.28 109.19 310.66 128 256 128H64c-35.35 0-64 28.65-64 64v96c0 35.35 28.65 64 64 64h33.7c-1.39 10.48-2.18 21.14-2.18 32 0 39.77 9.26 77.35 25.56 110.94 5.19 10.69 16.52 17.06 28.4 17.06h74.28c26.05 0 41.69-29.84 25.9-50.56-16.4-21.52-26.15-48.36-26.15-77.44 0-11.11 1.62-21.79 4.41-32H256c54.66 0 108.28 18.81 150.98 52.95l85.03 68.03a32.023 32.023 0 0 0 19.98 7.02c24.92 0 32-22.78 32-32V295.13C563.05 284.04 576 263.63 576 240zm-96 141.42l-33.05-26.44C392.95 311.78 325.12 288 256 288v-96c69.12 0 136.95-23.78 190.95-66.98L480 98.58v282.84z\"></path></svg> May 3rd Update - Easter Event has Arrived!</h5><div class=\"news-meta-row\"><span class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"svg-inline--fa fa-tags fa-w-20\" style=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" data-prefix=\"fas\" data-icon=\"tags\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 640 512\"><path class=\"\" style=\"\" fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M497.941 225.941L286.059 14.059A48 48 0 0 0 252.118 0H48C21.49 0 0 21.49 0 48v204.118a48 48 0 0 0 14.059 33.941l211.882 211.882c18.744 18.745 49.136 18.746 67.882 0l204.118-204.118c18.745-18.745 18.745-49.137 0-67.882zM112 160c-26.51 0-48-21.49-48-48s21.49-48 48-48 48 21.49 48 48-21.49 48-48 48zm513.941 133.823L421.823 497.941c-18.745 18.745-49.137 18.745-67.882 0l-.36-.36L527.64 323.522c16.999-16.999 26.36-39.6 26.36-63.64s-9.362-46.641-26.36-63.64L331.397 0h48.721a48 48 0 0 1 33.941 14.059l211.882 211.882c18.745 18.745 18.745 49.137 0 67.882z\"></path></svg> Announcements</span><span class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"svg-inline--fa fa-calendar fa-w-14\" style=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" data-prefix=\"fas\" data-icon=\"calendar\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\"><path class=\"\" style=\"\" fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M12 192h424c6.6 0 12 5.4 12 12v260c0 26.5-21.5 48-48 48H48c-26.5 0-48-21.5-48-48V204c0-6.6 5.4-12 12-12zm436-44v-36c0-26.5-21.5-48-48-48h-48V12c0-6.6-5.4-12-12-12h-40c-6.6 0-12 5.4-12 12v52H160V12c0-6.6-5.4-12-12-12h-40c-6.6 0-12 5.4-12 12v52H48C21.5 64 0 85.5 0 112v36c0 6.6 5.4 12 12 12h424c6.6 0 12-5.4 12-12z\"></path></svg> 05/04/2026 by <span class=\"news-author\"><svg class=\"svg-inline--fa fa-user fa-w-14\" style=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" data-prefix=\"fas\" data-icon=\"user\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\"><path class=\"\" style=\"\" fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M224 256c70.7 0 128-57.3 128-128S294.7 0 224 0 96 57.3 96 128s57.3 128 128 128zm89.6 32h-16.7c-22.2 10.2-46.9 16-72.9 16s-50.6-5.8-72.9-16h-16.7C60.2 288 0 348.2 0 422.4V464c0 26.5 21.5 48 48 48h352c26.5 0 48-21.5 48-48v-41.6c0-74.2-60.2-134.4-134.4-134.4z\"></path></svg><span class=\"news-author-name\">Bitterblade</span></span></span></div><div class=\"is-collapsed content\"><p>Greetings Trainers!<br/>\nThe Easter Event is live and Breezy Island can now be accessed by speaking with Sailor Richard in any port city.<br/>\n- Easter forms are huntable in all maps, except Pinkan Island. You can see a list of available Easter Forms on the <a href=\"https://wiki.pokemonrevolution.net/index.php?title=Pok%C3%A9mon_Counterparts#Easter-themed_Pok%C3%A9mon\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pokemon Counterparts Wiki page</a>.<br/>\n- Quality of Life Changes: Accurate descriptions for items and moves, items now show detailed information as well as if they are tradable or not, and additional GUI scale setting for the battle UI.<br/>\n- Finally, be sure to claim your <strong>limited-time</strong> redeem code, “CKA7-JVG8-DQXV-SFRB”, which expires on May 10, 2026!</p>\n\n<p>For a more detailed information on the changes, you can take a look at the <a href=\"https://pokemonrevolution.net/forum/topic/3146-update-logs/#findComment-1706428\" rel=\"nofollow\">Update Logs</a>.<br/>\nMake sure to join our <a href=\"https://discord.com/invite/98pMNxq\" rel=\"nofollow\">Discord server</a> to stay up to date with our news.</p>\n</div><button type=\"button\" class=\"news-toggle\"><svg class=\"svg-inline--fa fa-chevron-down fa-w-14\" style=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" data-prefix=\"fas\" data-icon=\"chevron-down\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\"><path class=\"\" style=\"\" fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M207.029 381.476L12.686 187.132c-9.373-9.373-9.373-24.569 0-33.941l22.667-22.667c9.357-9.357 24.522-9.375 33.901-.04L224 284.505l154.745-154.021c9.379-9.335 24.544-9.317 33.901.04l22.667 22.667c9.373 9.373 9.373 24.569 0 33.941L240.971 381.476c-9.373 9.372-24.569 9.372-33.942 0z\"></path></svg> Read more</button></article><article><h5 class=\"title\"><svg class=\"svg-inline--fa fa-bullhorn fa-w-18 title-icon\" style=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" data-prefix=\"fas\" data-icon=\"bullhorn\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 576 512\"><path class=\"\" style=\"\" fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M576 240c0-23.63-12.95-44.04-32-55.12V32.01C544 23.26 537.02 0 512 0c-7.12 0-14.19 2.38-19.98 7.02l-85.03 68.03C364.28 109.19 310.66 128 256 128H64c-35.35 0-64 28.65-64 64v96c0 35.35 28.65 64 64 64h33.7c-1.39 10.48-2.18 21.14-2.18 32 0 39.77 9.26 77.35 25.56 110.94 5.19 10.69 16.52 17.06 28.4 17.06h74.28c26.05 0 41.69-29.84 25.9-50.56-16.4-21.52-26.15-48.36-26.15-77.44 0-11.11 1.62-21.79 4.41-32H256c54.66 0 108.28 18.81 150.98 52.95l85.03 68.03a32.023 32.023 0 0 0 19.98 7.02c24.92 0 32-22.78 32-32V295.13C563.05 284.04 576 263.63 576 240zm-96 141.42l-33.05-26.44C392.95 311.78 325.12 288 256 288v-96c69.12 0 136.95-23.78 190.95-66.98L480 98.58v282.84z\"></path></svg> Battle Changes, Spawn Reworks, and More!</h5><div class=\"news-meta-row\"><span class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"svg-inline--fa fa-tags fa-w-20\" style=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" data-prefix=\"fas\" data-icon=\"tags\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 640 512\"><path class=\"\" style=\"\" fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M497.941 225.941L286.059 14.059A48 48 0 0 0 252.118 0H48C21.49 0 0 21.49 0 48v204.118a48 48 0 0 0 14.059 33.941l211.882 211.882c18.744 18.745 49.136 18.746 67.882 0l204.118-204.118c18.745-18.745 18.745-49.137 0-67.882zM112 160c-26.51 0-48-21.49-48-48s21.49-48 48-48 48 21.49 48 48-21.49 48-48 48zm513.941 133.823L421.823 497.941c-18.745 18.745-49.137 18.745-67.882 0l-.36-.36L527.64 323.522c16.999-16.999 26.36-39.6 26.36-63.64s-9.362-46.641-26.36-63.64L331.397 0h48.721a48 48 0 0 1 33.941 14.059l211.882 211.882c18.745 18.745 18.745 49.137 0 67.882z\"></path></svg> Announcements</span><span class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"svg-inline--fa fa-calendar fa-w-14\" style=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" data-prefix=\"fas\" data-icon=\"calendar\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\"><path class=\"\" style=\"\" fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M12 192h424c6.6 0 12 5.4 12 12v260c0 26.5-21.5 48-48 48H48c-26.5 0-48-21.5-48-48V204c0-6.6 5.4-12 12-12zm436-44v-36c0-26.5-21.5-48-48-48h-48V12c0-6.6-5.4-12-12-12h-40c-6.6 0-12 5.4-12 12v52H160V12c0-6.6-5.4-12-12-12h-40c-6.6 0-12 5.4-12 12v52H48C21.5 64 0 85.5 0 112v36c0 6.6 5.4 12 12 12h424c6.6 0 12-5.4 12-12z\"></path></svg> 04/24/2026 by <span class=\"news-author\"><svg class=\"svg-inline--fa fa-user fa-w-14\" style=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" data-prefix=\"fas\" data-icon=\"user\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\"><path class=\"\" style=\"\" fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M224 256c70.7 0 128-57.3 128-128S294.7 0 224 0 96 57.3 96 128s57.3 128 128 128zm89.6 32h-16.7c-22.2 10.2-46.9 16-72.9 16s-50.6-5.8-72.9-16h-16.7C60.2 288 0 348.2 0 422.4V464c0 26.5 21.5 48 48 48h352c26.5 0 48-21.5 48-48v-41.6c0-74.2-60.2-134.4-134.4-134.4z\"></path></svg><span class=\"news-author-name\">Shaolan</span></span></span></div><div class=\"is-collapsed content\"><p>Previously announced battle changes have made it out of testing and are now live! From Quality of Life adjustments to fresh spawn rotations, here is what’s happening in the world of Pokémon Revolution:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Battle Quality of Life:</strong> New changes regarding <strong>Choice items</strong> and <strong>locked moves</strong> (e.g., moves affected by Throat Chop, Psychic Noise, etc.) are now active. This update also includes many new abilities, items, and newly coded moves.<br/>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Spawn Reworks:</strong> Both <strong>Pinkan Island</strong> and <strong>Shadow Area</strong> have had their spawns updated. Various Pokémon have been removed, added, or shifted across these maps.<br/>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Ranked Rewards:</strong> Earn the <strong>Victorious Chroma</strong> for Celebi by placing in the <strong>Top 25</strong> of the Normal Ranked Ladder for the month of April.<br/>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Form Reworks:</strong> Summer forms for <strong>Latios</strong>, <strong>Latias</strong>, and <strong>Lapras</strong> have been reworked. Additionally, reworks are planned for the Summer Vanillite, Halloween Gligar, and Halloween Drilbur families.<br/>\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>For a more detailed breakdown of these changes, you can view the <a href=\"https://pokemonrevolution.net/forum/topic/3146-update-logs/page/25/#findComment-1705696\" rel=\"nofollow\">Update Logs</a> and the <a href=\"https://pokemonrevolution.net/forum/topic/217075-spawn-update-logs/page/2/#findComment-1686294\" rel=\"nofollow\">Spawn Update Logs</a>.</p>\n\n<p>Make sure to join our <a href=\"https://discord.gg/98pMNxq\" rel=\"nofollow\">Discord server</a> for news, updates, and more!</p>\n</div><button type=\"button\" class=\"news-toggle\"><svg class=\"svg-inline--fa fa-chevron-down fa-w-14\" style=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" data-prefix=\"fas\" data-icon=\"chevron-down\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\"><path class=\"\" style=\"\" fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M207.029 381.476L12.686 187.132c-9.373-9.373-9.373-24.569 0-33.941l22.667-22.667c9.357-9.357 24.522-9.375 33.901-.04L224 284.505l154.745-154.021c9.379-9.335 24.544-9.317 33.901.04l22.667 22.667c9.373 9.373 9.373 24.569 0 33.941L240.971 381.476c-9.373 9.372-24.569 9.372-33.942 0z\"></path></svg> Read more</button></article><!--]--></div></section></div></div></main></div><div class=\"footer-wrap\"><svg class=\"curve\" viewBox=\"0 0 400 50\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\"><path d=\"M400,50V21.7C266.6,6.1,133.4,6.1,0,21.7V50H400z\"></path></svg><footer class=\"app-footer\"><div class=\"page-container\"><div class=\"footer-grid\"><section class=\"footer-brand\"> Pokemon Revolution Online <ul class=\"languages\" aria-label=\"Language\"><!--[--><li class=\"active flag-icon-us flag-icon\" title=\"en\"></li><li class=\"flag-icon-fr flag-icon\" title=\"fr\"></li><li class=\"fl