vg class=\"svg-inline--fa fa-wikipedia-w fa-w-20\" style=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" data-prefix=\"fab\" data-icon=\"wikipedia-w\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 640 512\"><path class=\"\" style=\"\" fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M640 51.2l-.3 12.2c-28.1.8-45 15.8-55.8 40.3-25 57.8-103.3 240-155.3 358.6H415l-81.9-193.1c-32.5 63.6-68.3 130-99.2 193.1-.3.3-15 0-15-.3C172 352.3 122.8 243.4 75.8 133.4 64.4 106.7 26.4 63.4.2 63.7c0-3.1-.3-10-.3-14.2h161.9v13.9c-19.2 1.1-52.8 13.3-43.3 34.2 21.9 49.7 103.6 240.3 125.6 288.6 15-29.7 57.8-109.2 75.3-142.8-13.9-28.3-58.6-133.9-72.8-160-9.7-17.8-36.1-19.4-55.8-19.7V49.8l142.5.3v13.1c-19.4.6-38.1 7.8-29.4 26.1 18.9 40 30.6 68.1 48.1 104.7 5.6-10.8 34.7-69.4 48.1-100.8 8.9-20.6-3.9-28.6-38.6-29.4.3-3.6 0-10.3.3-13.6 44.4-.3 111.1-.3 123.1-.6v13.6c-22.5.8-45.8 12.8-58.1 31.7l-59.2 122.8c6.4 16.1 63.3 142.8 69.2 156.7L559.2 91.8c-8.6-23.1-36.4-28.1-47.2-28.3V49.6l127.8 1.1.2.5z\"></path></svg></a></div><button class=\"footer-link-button footer-cookie-button\" type=\"button\">Cookie settings</button></section><section>Policies <ul><li><a href=\"/en/disclaimer\" class=\"\">Disclaimer</a></li><li><a href=\"/en/privacy-policy\" class=\"\">Privacy Policy</a></li><li><a href=\"/en/terms-and-conditions\" class=\"\">Terms and Conditions</a></li><li><a href=\"/en/refund-policy\" class=\"\">Refund Policy</a></li></ul></section><section>Support <ul><li><a href=\"/en/faq\" class=\"\">FAQ</a></li><li><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://pokemonrevolution.net/forum/forum/34-general-support/\">Get Support</a></li><li><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://pokemonrevolution.net/forum/forum/4-suggestions/\">Suggestions</a></li><li><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://pokemonrevolution.net/forum/forum/37-general-complaint-area/\">Contact us</a></li></ul></section><section>Rules <ul><li><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://pokemonrevolution.net/forum/forum/161-pro-rules/\">PRO Rules</a></li><li><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://pokemonrevolution.net/forum/topic/62159-in-game-chat-rules/\">Chat Rules</a></li><li><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://pokemonrevolution.net/forum/topic/29538-overall-trade-rules-forums-and-in-game/\">Trade Rules</a></li><li><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://pokemonrevolution.net/forum/topic/31283-ranked-pvp-rules/\">PVP Rules</a></li></ul></section><section class=\"footer-logo\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><div class=\"logo\"></div></section></div></div><!----></footer></div></div></div>\r\n    <script>window.__PRO_INITIAL_STATE__={\"locale\":\"en\",\"latestNews\":[{\"id\":59,\"title\":\"July 8th, 2026\",\"author\":\"Bitterblade\",\"text\":\"\\u003cp>July brings big updates to the forums!\\u003cbr/>\\n* The new \\u003ca href=\\\"https://pokemonrevolution.net/forum/index.php?app=proauctions&amp;module=auction&amp;controller=auctions\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">Trade Zone\\u003c/a> is now live on the forums! This update brings a new, effecient way to navigate trades and features numerous, new filtering options. Please take some time to familarize yourself with these changes. The old Trade Zone will remain available until July 14 so that existing auctions can be completed, but it is no longer possible to start new threads there.\\u003cbr/>\\n* A World Quest starts July 11th during the day.\\u003cbr/>\\n* Tradable PvE Coin Shop items this month are: Salamence Mount, S Salamence Mount, Waluigi Hat, Waluigi Clothes\\u003c/p>\\n\\n\\u003cp>Make sure to join our \\u003ca href=\\\"https://discord.gg/98pMNxq\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">Discord server\\u003c/a> for news, updates, and more!\\u003c/p>\\n\",\"date\":\"2026-07-08T13:56:54Z\"},{\"id\":58,\"title\":\"Forum Upgrade: Invision 5 and Single Sign-On\",\"author\":\"Shaolan\",\"text\":\"\\u003cp>The forum has been upgraded from Invision 4 to Invision 5.\\u003cbr/>\\nThe upgrade to Invision 5 provides faster page load times, a modernized interface, and a improved responsive layout for mobile devices.\\u003c/p>\\n\\n\\u003ch4>Single Sign-On (SSO) &amp; Session Renewal\\u003c/h4>\\n\\n\\u003cp>The Dashboard, login system, and forum now share a single session. This eliminating the need for separate logins.\\u003c/p>\\n\\n\\u003ch4>Session Management\\u003c/h4>\\n\\n\\u003cp>Active sessions can now be managed from a single location. You can view or terminate active connections via the dashboard:\\u003c/p>\\n\\n\\u003cp>\\u003ca href=\\\"https://dashboard.pokemonrevolution.net/sessions\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">Dashboard Session page\\u003c/a>\\u003c/p>\\n\\n\\u003cp>To improve account safety, security actions such as a password change, will now automatically invalidate and log out all other active sessions.\\u003c/p>\\n\",\"date\":\"2026-07-06T10:01:33Z\"},{\"id\":57,\"title\":\"May 3rd Update - Easter Event has Arrived!\",\"author\":\"Bitterblade\",\"text\":\"\\u003cp>Greetings Trainers!\\u003cbr/>\\nThe Easter Event is live and Breezy Island can now be accessed by speaking with Sailor Richard in any port city.\\u003cbr/>\\n- Easter forms are huntable in all maps, except Pinkan Island. You can see a list of available Easter Forms on the \\u003ca href=\\\"https://wiki.pokemonrevolution.net/index.php?title=Pok%C3%A9mon_Counterparts#Easter-themed_Pok%C3%A9mon\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">Pokemon Counterparts Wiki page\\u003c/a>.\\u003cbr/>\\n- Quality of Life Changes: Accurate descriptions for items and moves, items now show detailed information as well as if they are tradable or not, and additional GUI scale setting for the battle UI.\\u003cbr/>\\n- Finally, be sure to claim your \\u003cstrong>limited-time\\u003c/strong> redeem code, “CKA7-JVG8-DQXV-SFRB”, which expires on May 10, 2026!\\u003c/p>\\n\\n\\u003cp>For a more detailed information on the changes, you can take a look at the \\u003ca href=\\\"https://pokemonrevolution.net/forum/topic/3146-update-logs/#findComment-1706428\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">Update Logs\\u003c/a>.\\u003cbr/>\\nMake sure to join our \\u003ca href=\\\"https://discord.com/invite/98pMNxq\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">Discord server\\u003c/a> to stay up to date with our news.\\u003c/p>\\n\",\"date\":\"2026-05-03T23:24:23Z\"},{\"id\":56,\"title\":\"Battle Changes, Spawn Reworks, and More!\",\"author\":\"Shaolan\",\"text\":\"\\u003cp>Previously announced battle changes have made it out of testing and are now live! From Quality of Life adjustments to fresh spawn rotations, here is what’s happening in the world of Pokémon Revolution:\\u003c/p>\\n\\n\\u003cul>\\n\\u003cli>\\u003cstrong>Battle Quality of Life:\\u003c/strong> New changes regarding \\u003cstrong>Choice items\\u003c/strong> and \\u003cstrong>locked moves\\u003c/strong> (e.g., moves affected by Throat Chop, Psychic Noise, etc.) are now active. This update also includes many new abilities, items, and newly coded moves.\\u003cbr/>\\n\\u003c/li>\\n\\u003cli>\\u003cstrong>Spawn Reworks:\\u003c/strong> Both \\u003cstrong>Pinkan Island\\u003c/strong> and \\u003cstrong>Shadow Area\\u003c/strong> have had their spawns updated. Various Pokémon have been removed, added, or shifted across these maps.\\u003cbr/>\\n\\u003c/li>\\n\\u003cli>\\u003cstrong>Ranked Rewards:\\u003c/strong> Earn the \\u003cstrong>Victorious Chroma\\u003c/strong> for Celebi by placing in the \\u003cstrong>Top 25\\u003c/strong> of the Normal Ranked Ladder for the month of April.\\u003cbr/>\\n\\u003c/li>\\n\\u003cli>\\u003cstrong>Form Reworks:\\u003c/strong> Summer forms for \\u003cstrong>Latios\\u003c/strong>, \\u003cstrong>Latias\\u003c/strong>, and \\u003cstrong>Lapras\\u003c/strong> have been reworked. Additionally, reworks are planned for the Summer Vanillite, Halloween Gligar, and Halloween Drilbur families.\\u003cbr/>\\n\\u003c/li>\\n\\u003c/ul>\\n\\n\\u003cp>For a more detailed breakdown of these changes, you can view the \\u003ca href=\\\"https://pokemonrevolution.net/forum/topic/3146-update-logs/page/25/#findComment-1705696\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">Update Logs\\u003c/a> and the \\u003ca href=\\\"https://pokemonrevolution.net/forum/topic/217075-spawn-update-logs/page/2/#findComment-1686294\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">Spawn Update Logs\\u003c/a>.\\u003c/p>\\n\\n\\u003cp>Make sure to join our \\u003ca href=\\\"https://discord.gg/98pMNxq\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">Discord server\\u003c/a> for news, updates, and more!\\u003c/p>\\n\",\"date\":\"2026-04-24T11:02:21Z\"}],\"detectedPlatformId\":null,\"auth\":{\"loggedIn\":false,\"profile\":null,\"mergeToken\":null,\"mergeTokenLoaded\":false,\"sessionNotice\":null}}</script>\r\r\n  </body>\r\n</html>\r\n"